title: Denis Fayzullin
text:
Denis Abudarovich Fayzullin (; born 12 April 2001) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="FC%20Fakel%20Voronezh">FC Fakel Voronezh</a> on loan from <a href="FC%20Lokomotiv%20Moscow">FC Lokomotiv Moscow</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Tom%20Tomsk">FC Tom Tomsk</a> on 27 February 2021 in a game against <a href="FC%20Alania%20Vladikavkaz%20%282019%29">FC Alania Vladikavkaz</a>.
On 1 June 2021, he extended his contract with <a href="FC%20Lokomotiv%20Moscow">FC Lokomotiv Moscow</a> and was loaned to <a href="FC%20Fakel%20Voronezh">FC Fakel Voronezh</a> for the 2021–22 season.
